see the craft to get an idea of if its Center of Mass and Center of Thrust are aligned.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-18T23:39:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso from the video timewarp wasn\u0027t actually working. The actual time to the node wasn\u0027t approaching faster. This hopefully would have shown up in the log file as an error\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ShroomTheVoice","CreatedById":227901,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-18T23:50:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224274338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216677\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221681859694\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022161238\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Anth12\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n34 minutes ago, Anth12 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nGame Save from the video\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nLog File\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nWhat Mods you are using\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks for that.\u00A0 I have other things to do today, I can replicate it, but quickly I can say now...\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nNO MODS!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}